{"tid":1201813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【字幕版】《WINTER OF FIRE : 烏克蘭自由之戰》【加少量分析】","createTime":"2019-06-11T06:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T10:11:25.000Z","uid":154486,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e21305ef0e2434d4f301c344af2723f523e03cc1","tid":1201813,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:33:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thisav.com/playvideo.php?videoid=425425&amp;page=%E5%87%9C%E5%86%AC%E7%83%88%E7%81%AB%EF%BC%9A%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thisav.com%2Fplayvideo.php%3Fvideoid%3D425425%26page%3D%25E5%2587%259C%25E5%2586%25AC%25E7%2583%2588%25E7%2581%25AB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2583%258F%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%2598%25AD%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2588%25B0.html&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=80ca874b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thisav.com/playvideo.php?videoid=425425&amp;page=%E5%87%9C%E5%86%AC%E7%83%88%E7%81%AB%EF%BC%9A%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0.html</a><br />\n<br />\n第一：烏克蘭開頭都係和理非非，有唱歌有玩膠，直到清場(10:00) <br />\n<br />\n第二：勇武派示威者開頭輸到貼地，開頭就算有部推土機(20:37) <br />\n夜左好多人冇防護比人打到仆街(22:00) <br />\n<br />\n第三：歐盟發言人講左兩句(33:00) ，之後就冇出過場<br />\n<br />\n第四：烏克蘭既差佬佈陣、裝備同香港冇大分別，唔係話特別勁或者廢<br />\n<br />\n第五：Slava Ukranini - Heroyem Slava係人所共知既口號，打招呼果陣、對峙果陣、衝果陣、葬禮果陣，都會大大聲講出黎，增強士氣<br />\n<br />\n第六：中段示威者已經有人係背後指揮，對峙時會不斷敲擊物件震懾(46:43) <br />\n<br />\n第七：<br />\n示威者組隊並且有自己既隊名(34:40) <br />\n學排陣 (34:55) <br />\n有人整左一批木盾(35:15) <br />\n中段左右好多人成功搶警察長鐵盾(45:50) <br />\n經訓練後由以前既散兵遊勇變成方陣<br />\n<br />\n第八：示威法過左之後，開始使用汽油彈同投擲硬物 (44:35)  <br />\n之前成功用滅火筒噴退攔路左膠 (44:12) <br />\n<br />\n第九：烏克蘭勇武派早中期冇特定形象領袖<br />\n<br />\n第十：第一位犧牲者年僅20（唔好死）<br />\n<br />\n第十一：烏克蘭廣場既地形係平地，但係後段警察已經有Sniper係大廈<br />\n<br />\n第十二：一位唔衝既小朋友參與調酒(47:10) <br />\n<br />\n第十三：黑社會藍屍(1:04:05) <br />\n<br />\n第十四：差佬已經癡左線，射醫護人士(51:30)，自己擲燃燒彈(1:08:55)<br />\n<br />\n重點係你以為戰鬥民族好威威，其實同你我經歷過既都冇大分別，點解咁快放棄<br />\n人地本身已有民主，都係打生打死先得到自由！！<br />\n人地有比人迫出黎既勇武<br />\n<img src=\"http://euromaidanpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/euromaidan_tires.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Feuromaidanpress.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Feuromaidan_tires.jpg&h=1ad91401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人地亦都有和理非非<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.rferl.org/0BC1A4DA-5EB0-4106-9548-107E82BA99DC_w1023_r0_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.rferl.org%2F0BC1A4DA-5EB0-4106-9548-107E82BA99DC_w1023_r0_s.jpg&h=ef675bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.kyivpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/06_AC8I1389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyivpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F06_AC8I1389.jpg&h=e6da4b40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cd9ca0cc363dd78d90683c2d3e7a2028fda0a71","tid":1201813,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a29d31ae984a6eab32fc261c1d8dda241c429d58","tid":1201813,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"013883d9891047e706027e289931171dc4bae63a","tid":1201813,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6cdf470c3fbf154114e11072d740f3c87a7c9fc","tid":1201813,"uid":139095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f32ed3462becba8a932c280d324f493169ae08","tid":1201813,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db26df10357397c29ec880e210d6b2d5d136bf9b","tid":1201813,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc5fc0e52842ea9dc9a2c4b9bed3f58766c74230","tid":1